{"tid":1028193,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【心理學】 3分鐘內告訴你如何透過安排減少拖延  及決策疲勞與拖延間的關係","createTime":"2019-02-19T10:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T13:57:24.000Z","uid":78029,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4dea94115304572a49d818cdedeedf2feb58ed58","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"大家好，小弟希望成為香港知識型Youtuber ，所以開咗一個Youtube Channel，希望我同大家可以一齊學吓唔同知識<br />\n希望大家比多D意見我改善, 因為我仲摸索緊個模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>今次講吓講吓決策疲勞同意志力間的關係, 希望可以幫助大家透過時間安排去減少拖延</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=65Gvi4ho6j8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D65Gvi4ho6j8&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=22a5740f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=65Gvi4ho6j8</a>"},{"pid":"bcdd4358c1ce53e5f32c2029c046dba259775f92","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:24:57.000Z","msg":"補充: <br />\n1. 本集取材於《Willpower: Rediscovering the Greatest Human Strength》, 《Making Choices Impairs Subsequent Self-Control: A Limited-Resource Account of Decision Making, Self-Regulation, and Active Initiative》,《 Extraneous Factors in Judicial Decisions》"},{"pid":"20309353c86fcd185f1db2bd83f63a3d90b4c7c4","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:25:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.非常感謝朋友T再次幫忙配音!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6239ef1f684ee28513097a97bbb3267d3e3cb85f","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"3. 其實另一個做法係減少做決定,  例如唔好襯衫, 着死一兩套<br />\n食野又係, 食死兩樣<br />\n不過咁會好慘, 同埋返工好難搞, 因為做野係被迫做決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ee12a95d8cbd