<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPxalLMq_gqw&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=e4b83c70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PxalLMq_gqw</a>"},{"pid":"fc37a07c3f78ec10529109edc9726394658458c1","tid":1028193,"uid":164583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"唔使多，教我點樣遠離手機<br />\n但我大多時間好依賴手機做野"},{"pid":"413dacbf0bc0de7e56d7b103a852222d20b56322","tid":1028193,"uid":223598,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"睇左第一條片<br />\n本身我都有睇開類似既頻道<br />\n但台灣同馬來多<br />\n我覺得幾好 時間係三分鐘到幾好消化<br />\n但我覺得某part語速有dd慢 成條片節奏好似變到唔鮮明<br />\n所有咁樣三分鐘好似內容量略小 可能今個題目本身小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋最後個段叫人睇個part 支咪好似差dd<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw幾好 加油 岩聽就聽 我個人覺得姐"},{"pid":"a0c1d8fa41e882ef127a2584ec30e8ca0c4fbef8","tid":1028193,"uid":65893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"lm遲下睇"},{"pid":"1684107759b70025478773a01a190b885e85937e","tid":1028193,"uid":71446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"如果見工個時做最尾個個，面試個位已經見左好多個，咁咪好易Fail?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495b9d2d69d1384d9bf3b7727268b73fa3116436","tid":1028193,"uid":130821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"呢招岩唔岩溝女用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab37c4e588577e3c5cd53b8bc609f79f192850c8","tid":1028193,"uid":130821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1684107759b70025478773a01a190b885e85937e","tid":1028193,"uid":71446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:52:17.000Z","ms