","msg":"點樣用智慧屌女?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打有無得分享?"},{"pid":"dbe767f35921c294f0a7a5655458d4cab1cce019","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d381e2faf1b9414696da1a5be0bbccdf3592834a","tid":1028193,"uid":182701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"拖延症末期患者here <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到個post掙扎左好耐<br />\n最後睇晒其他post先入黎留名<br />\n條片下次再睇（希望今日會睇）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"我仲有另外兩段片都講意志力, 遲D都會再講, 希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41aa6503d54203c1fd9e7c8c354ae2eb57c261f","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1d041f9389ff36cc3fab674b33d8e974bd3256c7","tid":1028193,"uid":37447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:44:18.000Z","msg":"內容幾好<br />\n但啲懶音真係好勁<br />\n講變左趕，而且語調好悶好冇生氣<br />\n然後成句句子讀得好唔連貫，好似一個一個字獨立跌出黎而非一段內容<br />\n明白旁白係義務幫手，但如果你要做YOUTUBER做得成功，吸引到人既旁白有時可能比你想PRESENT既內容更加重要，你可能要諗諗辦法，一係自己克服，一係搵個高手幫你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"多謝意見先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好過我本人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢今次係突登放慢, 一個字一個字咁讀, 因為怕有朋友聽唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然我地都會繼續改善, 會再研究, 語快語調同清晰中間拎平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162d7a6606c70e9a2acd5d206f16cd5c2db2186a","tid":1028193,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:21:01.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2e070b167601d32b2cc62dd1f4842f191d7a2fb9","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee031c531c023076f5805323c222404a6df8fb03","tid":1028193,"uid":52942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"我唔使一分鐘就夠<br />\n件事係唔係遲早都要做？<br />\n是&gt;儘快做<br />\n否&gt;有冇d遲早都要做既野<br />\n      有&gt;做左先<br />\n      沒有&gt; 做中意做既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"拖延症的朋友反而係知道有事遲早要做,  但選擇最尾先做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8637b8e8c9bee746e5f055a1ef3c998af6746960","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e81ceae037e1af876d3dda758bf9849a8175c4f1","tid":1028193,"uid":116967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"希望可以醫好拖延症<br />\n以前明明冇咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T05:24:04.000Z","msg":"絲打, 多謝繼續支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望幫到你<br />\n習慣咗某啲壞習慣的確難改D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回住咁多先, 有野做, 遲D再回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf97689ef7373a3f62734bceb4b46e77416933d","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7857a77c62acbf2f50a833929c329bab9a39ae4f","tid":1028193,"uid":164583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef923fc86b2e787a3071235fa371555713d4bbb","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc37a07c3f78ec10529109edc9726394658458c1","tid":1028193,"uid":164583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"唔使多，教我點樣遠離手機<br />\n但我大多時間好依賴手機做野"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"我會建議巴打你出過一部新但平+廢的手機 , 工作就用佢<br />\n呢一部手機只裝一D必要APP, 只用佢開WTSAPP入工作的GROUP<br />\n唔好要FB, GAME其他誘惑性的APP<br />\n<br />\n平時的一部就平時需要遠離的時候, 就放係一個見唔到的地方, 或者搵個信得過的人(親人朋友)KEEP住, 需要時先拎返<br />\n因為手機對你係誘惑, 如果比你見到就要用意志力去對抗, 咁一定會唔夠意志力用, 好快屈服, 所以一定要眼不見為乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然, 同時要定一個目標, 每日減少幾多分鐘, 記得循序漸進, 唔好一步登天, 每日減少少就夠<br />\n然後每日記低減少咗幾多非必要的手機使用時間, 比自己睇, 有個進步會鼓勵到自己<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T14:50:35.000Z","msg":"講開意志力<br />\n我睇書，話意志力每日一起身係滿電，<br />\n日間用下少d,用下少d，想點樣慳d用?<br />\n就係定規則。<br />\n而巴打建議既用第二部機既規則，<br />\n確實可幫我慳唔少腦汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"幫到你就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實原則好簡單, 開源節流<br />\n我三條講意志力都係講緊節流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲D講開源, 但開源較為難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d017392ce965f066076b02650882c5ceb00e4a","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93c22224ae580fc374aefbb0153c5a071f454b16","tid":1028193,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"你朋友咬字好過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n監獄個研究幾有趣, 應該值得更多讀政策既人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺應該多D心理學研究放入去政策到, 因為人的不理性應該要納入考慮, 先可以令世界更公平"},{"pid":"c0d8a1ac7bf870e5d40f3bfeb86faf9ed7922abe","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e40d3a3fe158c9d7fceab729f4e956a42c54b051","tid":1028193,"uid":130821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d769d2296ac2b0ce7a97007e6de7105d280064e","tid":1028193,"uid":78029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"495b9d2d69d1384d9bf3b7727268b73fa3116436","tid":1028193,"uid":130821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T10:59:41.000Z","msg":"呢招岩唔岩溝女用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder